Release Notes:

Pioneering metal act Dope are back with their 5th release and
first for KOCH Records. Led by front man Edsel Dope the band
have cemented themselves as a core metal act whos live
performances always leave the crowds knocked out. Sticking
with the heavier approach of their last release American
Apathy No Regrets shows the band continuing in a heavier
direction then their earlier material but with several singles
headed for active rock.

For fans of: Static-X, Drowning Pool, Powerman 5000
